The paper deals with hyperspectral imaging, which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses compressed sensing and sparse models, which are topics that fall under information theory (cs.IT) and mathematical modeling (cs.MM). The paper also discusses the use of spectral filters, which is a topic that falls under optics (cs.OH) and signal processing (cs.SI). Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.CV, followed by cs.IT, cs.MM, cs.OH, and cs.SI.
